    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "8fe42a8d_211c7cc8",
        "filename": "golden/go/tjstore/fs_tjstore/fs_tjstore.go",
        "patchSetId": 6
      },
      "lineNbr": 213,
      "author": {
        "id": 5395
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-09-06T18:45:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The docs say \"Do not modify application state inside of your transaction functions. Doing so will introduce concurrency issues\" so if I did something like that, it would require careful planning. I\u0027m not sure it\u0027s worth the implementation complexity at the moment - as I said, I believe the number of param maps to be relatively small.",
      "parentUuid": "fbeb9685_1ed8cef3",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 213,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 213,
        "endChar": 39
      },
      "revId": "3cf5dccca3072dd8e1ba36cbd575fb4fd92f7d49",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "40dac3f4_d5b84045",
