      },
      "lineNbr": 213,
      "author": {
        "id": 5120
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-09-09T16:29:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t understand your reply. I don\u0027t see any transaction here. I also don\u0027t see anything particularly complicated about using GetAll vs getting individually in a loop.\n\nFor Skia, currently the number of GroupParams will be at least 13, and will be more if additional tryjobs run. I would be pleasantly surprised if the queries are so fast that it doesn\u0027t make much difference if we run them one at a time or in a batch.",
      "parentUuid": "8fe42a8d_211c7cc8",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 213,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 213,
        "endChar": 39
      },
