      "writtenOn": "2019-09-06T18:45:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do we trust goldctl to have validated the params before uploading to the bucket?  If we can\u0027t trust data in the bucket, then this is not the layer to validate that (tryjob_ingestion would be).",
      "parentUuid": "e41a5207_6da48886",
      "range": {
